title: Chao Bian Zhan Tuo
synopsis: Super-changeable Zhanto is a brand new gyro sports that has swept the world! By superimposing the super ring on the main spinning top, the super variable battle spinning can instantly burst out miraculous explosive energy. In order to pursue the title of the strongest "Zhan Tuo King", gyro players from all over the world have gathered in the Zhan Tuo Academy to stage a passionate gyro duel! Turn left and right, start the strongest duel! ! ! Let's fight together!  (translated from iqiyi)

title: Chao Bian Zhan Tuo 2 Bao Jia Zhan Tuo
synopsis: After decades of development, Explosive Armor Battle Tuo duel has become one of the most popular sports in the world. At this time, the "Ultimate Feast" Invitational Tournament of Explosive Armored Warriors began. The protagonist Chen Xing is invited to the mysterious island together with other top warlords in the world to embark on a survival adventure. During the adventure, Chen Xing not only relied on his determination to guard the weak and gained recognition to unlock the power of the sacred beast, but also got acquainted with Ye Kong, a low-key expert who came here to find his brother, and the "perfect warrior" Le Zhengyang who wanted to prove to his father. . However, this "ultimate feast" is just a conspiracy of the organizer Stawan! He wants to use the warlords to awaken the evil forces in the island to destroy the world! The Chenxing trio stepped forward and tried their best to defeat Stawan. After the "ultimate feast", the three formed a dragon team to launch a sprint towards the championship team and the honor of the Explosive Zantuo King in the quadrennial Explosive Zantuo King Competition. Just one step from the highest honor was left after the trio of thorns and thorns. In the distant future, Stawan, who wanted to destroy the world, made a comeback...  (translated from iqiyi)

title: Chao Mini Zhanshi
synopsis: Can't get up? Can't remember reading? You have been invaded by troublesome stars! According to the tracking study of the most powerful brain girl in the universe, it turns out that human beings are not all inborn. It may be created by the troublesome star people of negative energy bodies! To defeat negative energy, one must rely on positive energy. So Doctor Girl created super mini fighters-Mini Brave and Mini Moe with courage and happiness as elements! They defeated the nasty troublesome stars with their super mini size and let people live a happy life again~ Do you also have countless troubles? Call the Super Mini Warrior! ! !  (translated from qq)

title: Chao Mini Zhanshi
synopsis: Too bad to run? Always forget the east and the west! It turns out that the troubles of humans may not be caused by themselves, but by the troubled stars! Fortunately, the baby girl doctor with an IQ of 500 used courage and happy energy to create "Super Mini Warrior" to help humans defeat troubles! Although he temporarily defeated the nasty Annoying Starman in the final battle, a new and more powerful Annoying Starman is here again. It is said that he never makes mistakes and is perfect! At the same time, Doctor Girl is facing a new challenge, with a red hair, the strongest primary school student on the surface appeared! Is he an enemy or a friend when he is aggressive? Faced with constantly emerging troubles and challenges, Mini Yong and Mini Moe have risen to the challenge, while working hard to evolve themselves, while constantly fighting for humanity! Are you worried? Quickly call the super mini warrior and defeat your troubles!  (translated from qq)

title: Dao Jian
synopsis: On January 9, 1943, under the instigation of the Japanese invaders, the Wang and Puppet government declared war on Britain and the United States, announcing that the soldiers and civilians in the area under the Wang and Puppet government would participate in the "holy war" promoted by the Japanese army. In order to accelerate the invasion and colonization of the land of China, the Japanese invaders vigorously advocated and built the "Greater East Asian Co-Prosperity Circle." Our story happened in the spring of this year, in a small town in the south of the Yangtze River called "Peach Blossom Town".  (translated from acfun)

title: Chao Zhineng Zuqiu 2: Shijie Dasai Pian
synopsis: Super Smart Football 2-World Series" is a teenage inspirational animation produced and distributed by Shenzhen Cube Animation Culture Development Co., Ltd. that combines "football competition", "future technology" and "humor and fun". In the 21st century, sports and technology are closely related. Sporting goods need the cooperation of science and technology. When designing footballs and football shoes, precise data and computer tests are needed to make some sporting goods that can exert human limits. If it is tested by humans, the state and technology must be deviated and unstable, so Dr. GGO was hired to assist in product development, and the GGO mechanical football player was born. With the rapid development of science and technology, the football competition has entered the unprecedented AI era-the football robot GGO, which is the size of a palm but has cutting-edge AI intelligence, was born! Fans all over the world are flocking! They have established their own GGO football teams and vowed to show their leading talents! The 13-year-old story protagonist Gao Xun accidentally got the unique seventh-generation GGO Qianlong invented by the father of a GGO expert, so he formed a "barefoot team" with his comrades to participate in the world GGO competition, and compete with other powers around the world. GGO football battle! At the same time, he secretly carried the hope of his father and led Qianlong to the finals to solve a little-known big conspiracy...  (translated from iqiyi)

title: Zhuang Zai Koudai Li De Baba
synopsis: Dad was not young at the beginning. He was just like the fathers of many other children, he was a sturdy man with a height of about 1.8 meters, five big and three thick. The reason why he gets smaller is because he is neither good at making money nor being an official, so he is often scolded by Yang Ge's mother. Every time his mother scolded him, his father's body shrank a little, and in the end he shrank to the size of his thumb. After getting smaller, his father's mind became very agile. He invented a series of things: cash cow, smart rice, dream maker, brainwashing gun, etc. These inventions brought earth-shaking changes to Yang Ge's family and the entire society. At the same time, terrorists also focused on his father's invention, and wanted to use his father's invention for evil. Can Yang Ge and his father defeat the terrorists and protect the earth? Peace and tranquility? (translated from iqiyi)

title: Ruguo Lishi Shi Yiqun Miao
synopsis: "If History is a Group of Meows" is a non-rigorous cute animation with Chinese history as the main line. The work reinterprets historical events in a humorous language, making it easier for young people to remember and accept. In terms of expression, the work uses modern animation techniques to shape 12 cats with abundance and cute shapes, and use them to interpret historical events into wonderful historical stories. The play not only responds to the call of the Central Committee on "Promoting Chinese Excellent Traditional Culture", but is also a new exploration and attempt of cultural innovation and "education through fun".  (translated from bilibili)

title: Da Zhonghua Xunbao Ji
synopsis: "Treasure Hunt in Greater China" is a 52-episode cartoon jointly produced by Shanghai Jingding Animation Technology Co., Ltd. and 21st Century Publishing Group. The cartoon was released on CCTV Children’s Channel (CCTV-14) on December 20, 2018. Premiere. The cartoon "Treasure Hunt in Great China" tells the story of a treasure hunting youth team composed of Mick, Guoguo, Yueban and others traveling through China with the five-element monsters, in Shanghai, Beijing, Tianjin, Chongqing, Shandong, and Sichuan. The thrilling and exciting treasure hunt story unfolded repeatedly. From Peking opera facial makeup, clay figurine Zhang Caishou to Confucius Temple, from Goubuli steamed buns, Beijing roast duck to Chongqing hot pot... These knowledge elements such as traditional Chinese culture and special cuisine are all integrated into the storyline, allowing the audience to follow the protagonist in the film In the adventurous footsteps, embarking on an enjoyable trip to China  (translated from iqiyi)

title: Blue Reflection Ray
synopsis: A clear summer sky spreads over the Hoshinomiya Girls' High School. This story begins with the belated start of school life for Hinako Shirai, who has just recovered from a leg injury due to a tragic accident. The magical sisters Yuzu and Lime bestowed her with a special power to become a "Reflector." Hinako transforms into the magical Reflector form and protects the world from devastating forces for the sake of the world, and her own dream that she thought she had to give up on. (Source: MAL News)

title: Yuzhou Huwei Dui
synopsis: "Guardians of the Universe" is an original three-dimensional animation series elaborately created by Perfect Kunpeng (Beijing) Animation Technology Co., Ltd. for children aged 4-7. The first season has 52 episodes, each with 12.5 minutes, launched in October 2018. The story of the first season revolved around the three members of the Space Guard, Tiger "Storm", Monkey "Lightning" and Rabbit "Rainbow". They are willing to help others and help different small animals solve various difficulties. Each episode covers knowledge points such as animal characteristics, life habits, and scientific knowledge, and encourages children to continue to grow through exploration. "Space Guard" conveys the positive energy of kindness, bravery, happiness and friendship, allowing children to follow the Space Guard to broaden their horizons, recognize creatures, and establish correct values in joy, so as to love our beautiful earth more.  (translated from iqiyi)

title: Yuzhou Huwei Dui
synopsis: Guardians of the Universe 2 is here! Guardians of the Universe 2 has 26 episodes, each with 12.5 minutes. In addition to the upright and brave Captain Tiger Storm, the natural activist Monkey Lightning, and the knowledgeable and intelligent rabbit Rainbow, the team members ushered in new players. ——Mechanic Expert Piggy Meteor. More intense rescue, more interesting plot, more tacit cooperation, "Guardians of the Universe 2" looks forward to your joining together!  (translated from iqiyi)

In the new season, they cooperated better with the new team member-Piggy Meteor, and continued to explain more new friends. With more intense rescue, more interesting plot, and richer knowledge, "Guardians of the Universe Season 3" will take you on a new adventure together!  (translated from iqiyi)

title: Menghuan Senlin
synopsis: This is a humorous, hilarious and touching story with a group of cute elves in the forest as the protagonist.  (translated from iqiyi)

title: He Jing Shaonian
synopsis: From the research results of his grandfather, Le Bao discovered that the metal age once existed in ancient times, and awakened the creatures of the metal age, Liao of the Cumlong clan. The earth's energy has been nearly exhausted due to human greed and plunder, but the greedy Sigma Energy Group does not hesitate to destroy the environment and ecology in order to obtain nuclear crystal fragments. The warriors of the Lebao and Collon clan went all over the world to rescue the earth's ecology and collect and protect nuclear crystal fragments. In the process of fighting against Lebao, Feifan found that Sigma Energy Group had tampered with his own memory, so he separated from Sigma Group and led his companions of the Cumlong clan to pursue the nucleus crystal fragments. Under the three-way wrestling, the competition for nucleus crystal fragments became fierce. Feifan got his own nucleus crystal fragments, and gradually learned to care about the fate of his companions and mankind.  (translated from iqiyi)

title: San Zhi Songshu
synopsis: "Three Squirrels" tells the story of three little squirrels coming to the human world, accidentally hitting and entering a nut shop, giving the owner courage and confidence, helping him find his true self, for dreams, for friends, and to change himself into a squirrel man. Together with Squirrelman, we use kindness and justice to drive away the evil forces and assume the responsibility of maintaining the safety of the entire city.  (translated from youku)

title: San Zhi Songshu Zhi Songshu Xiao Zhen
synopsis: The three squirrels came to the town and became good friends with the young Zhang Guoguo in the town, and used the squirrel bracelet brought from Squirrel World to transform Zhang Guoguo into a superhero.  (translated from youku)

title: San Zhi Songshu Zhi Songshu Xiao Zhen 2
synopsis: The three squirrels came to Squirrel Town from the forest, met Zhang Guoguo, a teenager in Squirrel Town, and helped Zhang Guoguo collect scattered squirrel bracelet fragments to regain the ability to transform into a superhero Squirrelman. In the battle with the evil forces headed by Boss Ann, Xiaoku set back the time and made the town a whole new look. In the new town, the three squirrels and Zhang Guoguo set up a squirrel rescue team to maintain the daily operations of the town, help the people in need of Squirrel Town, and constantly deal with boss An and his follower Bobcats who want to get attention. Out of trouble. In the process of dealing with the problem, the Squirrel Rescue Team showed everyone the fantasy style of Squirrel Town on the one hand, and also allowed people to experience the humanistic care in the town service.  (translated from qq)

title: San Zhi Songshu Zhi Zhongguo Xing
synopsis: The story takes place in China. There is a mysterious island in the East China Sea, called Wish Island. As long as you send a letter to Wish Island, there will be a mysterious little angel to help you realize your wish, and this mysterious little angel is a squirrel. Task force. Every day, at the task force base on Wish Island, Captain Zhang Guoguo will receive a wish letter from all over China. After receiving this wish letter, Zhang Guoguo will send a squirrel task force to the sending place , To help the children there to realize their wishes. Each member of the Squirrel Task Force has their own unique abilities, and they will use their unique abilities to work together to solve problems. However, only children can see Task Force Squirrel. Adults will not believe the task force, and Task Force Squirrel must complete various tasks without letting adults see themselves.  (translated from youku)

title: Zhuanzhan Zhi Chao Xuan Doushi
synopsis: The story is about the protagonist Yuecheng who aspires to become a hero accidentally get a magical turn. By chance, Yuecheng discovered the used super-spinning life form and the evil pen hunting organization. In order to rescue these trapped super-spinning creatures and stop the evil hunting pen organization, Yuecheng joined the "justice front" and met the lovable girl Sun Milulu, the brave and honest Li Zijie, and the cold Chen Cangdu , And Su Yongye, who also has a dual personality, manic on the surface but with great wisdom in his heart. Finally, after a series of arduous battles, Yuecheng and his party successfully resolved the crisis and exchanged peace for the city. Yuecheng also gained everyone’s approval. , Became a hero recognized by everyone. (translated from bilibili)

title: Zhuanzhan Chao Xuan Doushi Chao Xuan Juexing
synopsis: The story tells the story of a young Yuecheng who loves to turn the pen, meets the super spinning life form "flaming soul" through spinning, and gains its power, becoming a super spinning fighter against evil. In the process, Yuecheng encountered various evil super-spinning fighters. To satisfy their selfish desires, they committed many incidents that endangered the order. In order to fight against these evildoers, Yuecheng was determined to become a hero of justice and to eliminate evil with his companions. In the interesting incidents related to pen-turning, Yuecheng gradually pondered how to become a qualified hero and constantly pursue his heroic dreams.  (translated from iqiyi)

details.Japanese: 转战超旋斗士超旋觉醒

title: Hen Xiyou season2
synopsis: The four masters and apprentices of Tang Seng returned from the scriptures and returned to Datang. Unexpectedly, a powerful enemy of unknown origin stole the scriptures on the way. Monkey King lost his surviving son in a battle with the enemy and almost died. The whereabouts of the four masters and apprentices are unknown. In the 21st century, Fu He, an ordinary high school student, accidentally fell from a high altitude and was possessed by the soul of Monkey King. Two completely different souls were put in a piece of waste wood. How will Wukong whose life is threatened survive in this world? Where, what will happen to his life as the waste firewood who was possessed by Monkey King pays his congratulations...  (translated from iqiyi)

title: 0 Hao Sushe
synopsis: Freshmen often win by mistakes and come to dormitory 0. The fantasy of beautiful campus life did not come as expected, but three roommates who hadn't graduated for ten thousand years came like a nightmare: the rich black cat Edison, the irritable raccoon Jia Hero, and the weird hedgehog Ruan Xiang. Fall into the abyss. The four partners are together, causing trouble, doing things, laughing and tearing, sharing joys and sorrows. Will the pure and ever-victorious realize his dream? Will the three "weirds" turn to the sun and find the meaning and direction of life?  (translated from bilibili)

title: Baosu Heti
synopsis: One day, a huge crack suddenly appeared in the midair of the city, followed by mechanical monsters attacking the city. Le Tianxiang, a passionate young man who wanted to become a hero, also unexpectedly partnered with the explosive Mecha Lingkong in this attack, and defeated the enemy with the joint efforts of the two. Since then, mechanical monsters have attacked the city one after another. In the process of fighting against the enemy, Le Tianxiang and Lingkong also met and became acquainted with their friends and partners, including Shi Dagang, a simple and warm boy, Si Xiaosu who is a big ghost, and handsome and elegant Duanmuhai. teammate. Moreover, everyone also discovered some connections between these attackers, and there seems to be a stronger manipulator behind them! Just as everyone was preparing to conduct an in-depth investigation, Le Tianxiang's class came to a mysterious transfer student Fang Fal who also had an explosive mecha partner. Since Fang Falcon joined the team, the enemy’s mechanical monsters always seem to be able to attack everyone’s weaknesses. (translated from iqiyi)

title: Mengshou Zhan Jing
synopsis: In the world of alien beasts, the Lightning Tiger Willie of the Beastmen, Amy the Gale Eagle, and Dono the Ice Crocodile use traps to fight against the brutal beasts who like to destroy. However, in order to create an environment suitable for its survival, Descartes, the leader of the brutal beasts, led the brutal beasts to the earth. The beautiful happy town is facing the crisis of environmental destruction! In order to stop its conspiracy, the Beastmen chased to Happy Town, but they lost their original strength. Fortunately, they met human children Wu Xiaotian, Ally Li, and Lin Xiaobao. They teamed up to get the power of environmental protection and upgrade again; and You also get the power of the high-level beasts and police to explode Thunder Dragon Aaron, and the combination upgrade becomes more powerful! The angry Descartes finally summoned the savage beast god of war, but under the common goal of protecting the environment and protecting the happy town, the savage beasts burst out with great power, the beasts tiger king, gale eagle king, and ice crocodile king upgraded to A new form, together purifying Descartes  (translated from iqiyi)

title: Dan Dan Xiaozi
synopsis: On July 7, 2018, in order to retrieve the mysterious substance on the planet Dandan, the Orega substance, the Dandan starmen forced a landing on the earth after chasing the steel. Due to the carelessness of the villain's steel, the Orega substance has penetrated into the earth's coins and scattered everywhere. In order to retrieve Oregal's material, the Dandan Stars are in a situation where they must fight alone. At this time, as long as the coins infiltrated with Origa's substance are put into the vending machine, various monsters such as can monsters and snack monsters will pop out of them. Under the orders of the bluffing universe villain Gang Jun, the silly monsters find fault with the Dandan star in everything and prevent them from completing their mission. To make matters worse, they were mistaken for toys by children on the earth, threatening to be kidnapped. Finally, I had a fateful meeting with the earth boy Xiao Ming... These little aliens actually took the huge earth boy Xiao Ming as a prisoner, and called them at will. Despite this, the kind-hearted Xiao Ming still provides a house for the poor ultra-mini aliens... sure enough, can these mini-dandan boys break through the barriers of the universe villains and silly monsters and find Oliega again What about matter? And avoid the sight of the people on earth and successfully complete the mission? (translated from iqiyi)

title: Dan Dan Xiao Zi Zhi Dan Xing Xia
synopsis: The universe’s super-powerful special attack team-the "Egg Starman" received a secret mission, which is to transfer the energy of the most mysterious and precious substance in the universe. Unexpectedly, on the way, they were attacked by the cosmic villain who coveted Origa's energy and fell to the earth. Finally, the "Egg Starman" made an emergency landing near a toy store in Shanghai, China! However, the huge impact generated during the emergency landing caused the Orega energy in the spacecraft to fall out, and as a result, he was mistakenly swallowed by a terrestrial boy. The problem is that the energy of Orija will be affected by people's mental state! In order to prevent the deterioration of Oriega's energy and let the earthling boys maintain good living habits, the "Egg Starman" has launched a 24-hour close surveillance operation on the boy... Can the'Egg Starman' protect Oriega's energy? ?  (translated from iqiyi)

Both brothers and sisters go to school in "Dexin Academy". The play revolves around the siblings, parents, teachers and friends around them. Each episode is a short story from the perspective of the child's clear eyes and innocent soul, covering social, human relations, environmental protection, survival, belief and other issues from a small view, subtly popularizing the spiritual core of "love, beauty, and responsibility".  (translated from iqiyi)

synopsis: After the ultimate battle with the cursed evil god, in order to completely destroy the dragon army and protect the world, the super-changing braves boarded the Penguin battleship and arrived at a brand new city-Xinsi City. Dr. Leo built a secret base in Xinsi City. Yaoyao operates the central control center to monitor all corners of the world in real time. Once an emergency caused by the Dragon Legion occurs, an alarm will be issued and the super-changing brave will be dispatched for execution. task. In the secret base, Dr. Leo has developed a battle armor that can greatly enhance the power of the super-changeable God of War! It can be used as a vehicle for everyone to carry out tasks, and it can be perfectly integrated with the Super Change God of War, so that the Super Change God of War is upgraded to a more powerful form. So the super-changing brave and the teachers settled down in the secret base, constantly training and learning, and at the same time shouldering the task of guarding Xinsi City. The new leader of the dragon army, Uta, transformed his dragons into the appearance of ordinary humans, sneaking into the city silently and constantly creating chaos. At the same time, Uta is also planning a new dark plan, trying to create a secret weapon with powerful destructive power. Can the super-changing brave stop the turmoil in every corner of the city and destroy the dragon army's plan for world hegemony? (translated from iqiyi)

The project gave full play to the lively and imaginative performance characteristics of the cartoon. It used the historical events of the Western Han Dynasty Zhang Qian’s mission to the Western Regions and the first opening of the Silk Road as the material; the perspective of a pair of modern brothers passing through the audience, Experience the legendary process of Special Envoy Zhang Qian's mission to the Western Regions and the opening of a new era of cultural exchanges between the East and the West  (translated from iqiyi)

Although Yang Laixi was young but dexterous and agile, as a soldier in the detective squad, he repeatedly found out important enemy situations and helped the people of eastern Zhejiang fight against the Japanese and puppet forces. When helping the wounded to move their positions, Yang Laixi was seen through by a traitor. In order to avoid the New Fourth Army wounded from being found, Yang Laixi even took the puppet and fell to the cliff and was seriously injured. After being rescued by the villagers, Yang Laixi recovered his injuries I did not forget to actively contact the large army and organize an anti-Japanese team in the village to take the villagers to resist the Japanese invaders.  (translated from iqiyi)

In the future many years later, in order to activate the "seven-color flower" that supports the energy core of the future city, the young Hangdang and Xiaoyu use the space-time shuttle to come to the seven traditional Chinese festivals of the Spring Festival, Lantern Festival, Qingming Festival, Dragon Boat Festival, Qixi Festival, Mid-Autumn Festival and Chongyang Festival. Collecting energy in this activity activates the seven-color petals representing blessings, remembrance, remembrance, loyalty, reunion, respect for the elderly, and celebration, shattering Dr. Delhi’s conspiracy to replace humans with machine life and continuing the cultural and emotional roots of the future city. title: Chaoji Yi Zi
synopsis: In the vast universe, there is a gourmet planet called Kukkaka. On the planet, the gourmet elf Yizi and his friend Tuwanzi accidentally came to the earth through the four-dimensional black hole and were saved by the children of the earth, Alan and Yami. Yi Zi and Alan became good friends. Yizai possesses the food abilities that can bring happiness and joy to people. The owner of Food City, Mu, finds that Yizai's food can awaken his lost sense of taste, so he wants to catch Yizai. I didn't expect Xiao Yizi to transform into a super Yizi, and with the help of Alan and Yami, he repeatedly frustrated Boss Mu's arrest plan! In the process of Boss Mu hunting down Yizi, Ellen, Yizi, Boss Mu and his men were accidentally involved in a black hole and returned to the planet Kukkaka. On the novel and beautiful planet of Kuka, there are many funny and interesting stories between Boss Mu and the food elves! Adapted from the "Influenza" scientific masterpiece "Influenza Virus: The Enemy That Can't Hide" led by Gao Fu, an academician of the Chinese Academy of Sciences and director of the Chinese Center for Disease Control and Prevention. The cartoon "Influenza Virus" tells the story of the three little protagonists Kujie, Anna, and Confused Cai entering some magical world that can reproduce the history of the virus and the inside of the human body, and fight heroically against the virus army inside. Every short story in the play is easy to understand and entertaining, so that people can understand the influenza virus in an all-round way and teach scientific methods to deal with influenza.  (translated from iqiyi)

If it is true, protect it. After the three arrived, the dragon was discovered, but it was not a natural dragon, but it was made by genetic modification by two scientists. This dragon is cute and kind, and the three of them like it very much. But one morning, countless livestock in the village died in a pool of blood, and a three-year-old boy was also missing. Everyone said it was a one-stop job and decided to kill it. The three of Kujie didn't believe that Long did it, but they all pointed to the same murderer. The three Kujie decided to join the villager organization, one is to protect the dragon secretly and avoid being killed, and the other is to find the truth of the matter. (translated from iqiyi)

The story tells the story of a 12-year-old Qiwei who wanted to become a small agent in the secret service base. By chance, he successfully entered the base and became a small agent. Just when Qi Wei felt lucky that he was lucky, a series of incredible things happened. Monsters living in the mirror raided the base, vampires and werewolves appeared in the city, and then residents, a large number of agents and even commanders disappeared. The remaining agents discovered through monitoring that these mysterious incidents were related to Wei Wei. Wei Wei was detained and awaiting trial, but Wei Wei was completely puzzled and did not know who he was used by. (translated from iqiyi)

He wanted to get help from his parents, but his parents did not pay attention to Yimin's emotional abnormality at work. As Niu Chongtian's challenge to Yimin intensified, Yimin's personality became withdrawn and closed. She repeatedly endured it, and the situation became worse. Just when she was about to compromise her fate, she saw the unknown side of Niu soaring to the sky, and her fate has since changed.  (translated from iqiyi)

title: Tai Lao Niangniang Yu Baicha Xianzi
synopsis: "Grandma Empress and White Tea Fairy" tells the story of Taima Mountain on the coast of the East China Sea, which is surrounded by clouds and mist and is full of strange stones. Thousands of years ago, the mother of Emperor Yao used tea to treat illnesses in this mountain, and was regarded as the grandmother's wife by the people. However, the beautiful mountain has been eroded and destroyed by humans. Seeing that the vegetation has been cut and burned, the elves and beasts have been displaced, and the benevolent grandmother has opened up an independent space in the mountains --- the secret realm of the grandma, for those who have nowhere to shelter. The elves and beasts provided shelter. Later, from the old white tea tree that she once planted, the grandmother got the old tree spirit --- white The help of tea fairy. They began to wander in the mountains, looking for ways to connect to the secret realm. As long as they can engrave the mark of harmony in the hearts of the spirits of Taimu Mountain and the people at the foot of the mountain, and smooth various contradictions, the spirits and humans will catalyze the light of "harmony", and this will to "coexist in harmony" can neutralize The concept of "isolated world" in the secret realm brings the secret realm back to reality (translated from baidu baike)

Therefore, there are new things to play, learn, and explore every day. The five Wowo Babes use their expertise in the five fields of leadership, science, machinery, sports, and art to help each other and reserve the skills needed to explore the new world. They hope to team up to drive their own spacecraft to travel the sky in the future. Visit other planets.  (translated from iqiyi)

Can Cuckoo become the next queen? What kind of growth will Xiao Ai and Xiao Ni get during their travels?  (translated from iqiyi)
